- title: Are you ready to apply for an ADU?
  fields:
  - label: |
      This application will ask you about:

      - The builder's and owner's contact information

      - Property details like use and occupancy codes

      - Construction details like estimated costs, excavation area, all planned changes, and seismic work

      - Legal requirements like workers’ compensation insurance policy coverage

      Finally you will upload your plans as PDFs and agree to our legal terms.

      Unless you are building the ADU yourself, you will need a professional to fill out this form. If you have not yet hired a architect, contractor or engineer licensed in California, you should do so before you apply.
    type: paragraph

- title: About you
  fields:
  - label: First name
    annotation: PRJ and Joint Checklist (Planning), G-23 Attachment B, Authorized Agent Disclosure and Owner / Builder Disclosure (DBI) 

  - label: Last name
    annotation: PRJ and Joint Checklist (Planning), G-23 Attachment B, Authorized Agent Disclosure and Owner / Builder Disclosure (DBI)

  - group: non-owner
    fields:
    - label: Relationship to owner
      type: radio
      annotation: PRJ and Joint Checklist (Planning), Authorized Agent Disclosure (DBI)
      options:
      - label: I am the owner
        shows: owner

      - label: Architect
        shows: non-owner

      - label: Contractor
        shows: non-owner

      - label: Engineer
        shows: non-owner

      - label: Attorney
        shows: non-owner
      other: yes

    - group: non-owner
      fields:
      - label: California license number
        maxlength: 12
        annotation: Form 3/8 and Authorized Agent Disclosure (DBI)

      - label: License expiration date
        type: date
        annotation: Form 3/8 and Authorized Agent Disclosure (DBI)

- title: Owner consent
  group: owner
  fields:
  - type: paragraph
    label: |
      If you are building this ADU yourself, check the box below.

      If not, you will need to ask a professional to fill out this form for you.

  - label: I, the owner, am building this ADU myself.
    type: checkbox
    shows: owner-builder

- title: About you
  fields:
  - label: Contact information
      type: header
      level: 2
     
  - label: Name of your organization
    optional: yes
    annotation: Authorized Agent Disclosure (DBI) 

  - group: non-owner
    fields:
    - label: Mailing address
      type: address
      annotation: PRJ (Planning), G-23 Attachment B, Form 3/8, Authorized Agent Disclosure and Owner / Builder Disclosure (DBI)

  - label: Phone number
    type: phone
    annotation: PRJ and Joint Checklist (Planning), G-23 Attachment B, Form 3/8, Authorized Agent Disclosure and Owner / Builder Disclosure (DBI)

  - label: Email
    type: email
    annotation: PRJ and Joint Checklist (Planning), G-23 Attachment B, Form 3/8 and Authorized Agent Disclosure (DBI)

- title: Property
  group: non-owner
  fields:
   - label: Owner information
      type: header
      level: 2

  - label: Who owns the property?
    type: radio
    options:
    - label: "A person"
      shows: owner-person

    - label: "An organization"
      shows: owner-org

- title: "The property: Owner's information"
  group: non-owner
  fields:
  - group: owner-org
    fields:
    - label: Name of organization
      annotation: PRJ (Planning), Form 3/8 and Authorized Agent Disclosure (DBI)

  - group: owner-person
    fields:
    - label: Owner's first name
      annotation: PRJ (Planning), Form 3/8 and Authorized Agent Disclosure (DBI)

    - label: Owner's last name
      other: yes
      annotation: PRJ (Planning), Form 3/8 and Authorized Agent Disclosure (DBI)

  - label: Owner's phone number
    type: phone
    optional: yes
    annotation: PRJ (Planning), Form 3/8 and Authorized Agent Disclosure (DBI)  

  - label: Owner's email address
    type: email
    annotation: PRJ (Planning), Form 3/8 and Authorized Agent Disclosure (DBI) 
 
- title: "The property: Owner’s address"
  fields:
  - label: Owner's mailing address
    type: address
    annotation: PRJ (Planning), Authorized Agent Disclosure (DBI) 

  - label: Is this also the address of the ADU project?
    type: radio
    options:
    - label: "Yes"

    - label: "No"
      shows: project-address
    annotation: If "yes," populate "Project address" with the mailing address

  - group: project-address
    fields:
    - label: Project address
      type: address
      annotation: PRJ (Planning); G-23 Attachment B, Form 3/8, Authorized Agent Disclosure and Owner / Builder Disclosure (DBI)
      address-fields:
      - 'street'
      - 'zip'

    - label: Block and lot
      annotation: G-23 Attachment B and Form 3/8 (DBI)
      hidden: yes

- title: "The property: Use codes"
  fields:
  - label: What are the building's current use codes?
    annotation: Form 3/8 (DBI)
    type: checkbox
    options:
    - label: "10: Office"
    - label: "24: Apartment"
    - label: "27: 1 Family Dwelling"
    - label: "28: 2 Family Dwelling"
    - label: "79: Vacant Lot"
    - label: "Other"
      shows: present-use-other

  - group: present-use-other
    fields:
    - label: Enter any building use codes that are not listed above. 

  - label: Will the building's use codes change after construction?
    type: radio
    annotation: DBI and Planning
    options:
    - label: "Yes"
      shows: proposed-use-codes

    - label: "No"

  - group: proposed-use-codes
    fields:  
  - label: What will the building’s use codes be after construction?
    annotation: Form 3/8 (DBI)
    type: checkbox
    options:
    - label: "10: Office"
    - label: "24: Apartment"
    - label: "27: 1 Family Dwelling"
    - label: "28: 2 Family Dwelling"
    - label: "79: Vacant Lot"
    - label: "Other"
      shows: proposed-use-other

  - group: proposed-use-other
    fields:
    - label: Enter any proposed building use codes that are not listed above. 

