- title: "The property: Environmental assessment"
  fields:

  - label: |
      If your site is over 1,500 square feet or has: 

      - A current or former gas station

      - A parking lot

      - An auto repair shop

      - Dry cleaners

      - Heavy manufacturing use

      - Underground storage tanks

      You need to provide an environmental site assessment after you apply.
    type: paragraph

  - label: Does the site have any of the above?
    type: radio
    annotation: PRJ (Planning)
    options:
    - label: "Yes"
      shows: environmental-assessment

    - label: "No"

