  - group: maher
    fields:
    - type: header
      label: Maher ordinance waiver
      level: 4

    - label: |
        If you are in a Maher area, you will need to  [apply for a Maher Ordinance waiver](https://www.sfdph.org/dph/EH/HazWaste/hazWasteSiteMitigation.asp)

        To learn whether this applies to you, consult our [map of Maher areas](https://sfplanninggis.org/pim/map.html?layers=Maher%20Ordinance). 
      type: paragraph

  - type: header
    level: 4
